data.description: Welcome home to this amazing move in ready end of group townhouse in Perryville MD. This home features 3160 square foot living space one of the biggest townhomes in Cecil County. The main level features a large living room, half bath, main floor laundry, updated kitchen, large dining room with beautiful vaulted ceiling large propane fireplace with stone mantel, massive first floor master suite with amazing windows with a walkout deck Walkin closet and large bathroom with soaker tub and standalone shower. Second floor features 2 large bedrooms with full bath as well as a common area that could be closed off to make an extra bedroom. The lower level features a massive basement used as a theater room, another full bath and large storage area. This home also features a large garage with access into the home.   This home is minutes from the Susquehanna River with boat launch ramp, walking trail and beautiful views. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this beautiful home. Home was just freshly painted and ready for the new owner.
